        "text": "猛",
        "label": "PER"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_013_053_000039",
    "sentence": "欲乘間擒猛自為功，乃誘猛走歸順。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "猛",
        "label": "PER"
      },
